profile:
Matt and Tim, the founders of Clean Ducts Ottawa, are twin brothers who are both experienced TSSA gas technicians.

They take pride in the residential duct cleaning industry in Ottawa and are always looking for the best ways to serve the consumer.

Both Matt and Tim have served their country; Matt served 3 years in the Canadian forces, in the infantry. Tim served overseas, in Afghanistan, as a contractor for the military.

Matt and Tim are professional and hardworking individuals and value integrity as their highest standard when it comes to providing air quality services to help homeowners breathe cleaner air.
